# QEMU starts
 ├─ creates machine + devices (prepate the hardware)
 ├─ builds MemoryRegion tree (mtree)
 ├─ builds device object graph (qtree)
 │
 ├─ loads firmware (SeaBIOS / OVMF)
 │    ├─ scans PCI config space
 │    ├─ assigns BARs
 │    ├─ builds ACPI / E820 tables
 │
 └─ jumps to firmware entry point

# qtree != firmware device tree
# its qemu specific
(qemu) info qtree
info qtree
